27:42.135 --> 27:44.970
Okay.

27:45.004 --> 27:47.639
This is the story ball.

27:47.674 --> 27:49.942
When you hold it, you have

27:49.976 --> 27:52.511
the power over the story.

27:52.545 --> 27:55.514
Okay? Oh wait, I see...

27:55.548 --> 27:58.550
You have to sign and hold the
ball... that's not gonna work.

27:58.585 --> 28:00.786
So okay.

28:02.422 --> 28:03.522
