28:03.556 --> 28:05.657
- an imaginary ball. Yeah?
-_

28:07.594 --> 28:11.163
All right, here, Bay, catch!

28:12.165 --> 28:15.534
Okay, uh... once there was

28:15.568 --> 28:18.370
a girl named Juliet

28:18.405 --> 28:21.140
and she did not want to

28:21.174 --> 28:25.043
marry the guy she was supposed to marry...

28:27.380 --> 28:30.115
<i>Interpreter: "So she got into a spaceship</i>

28:30.150 --> 28:32.084
and starts heading off into space."

28:32.118 --> 28:34.720
"We're not talking about
going off into space!

28:34.754 --> 28:36.188
That's stupid."

28:38.691 --> 28:41.059
<i>"The Soviet Union? That wasn't stupid?"</i>

28:41.094 --> 28:42.795
Wait, hold it, hold it.

28:42.829 --> 28:45.964
We don't use the word
"stupid"! All ideas are welcome!

28:45.999 --> 28:48.567
Come on, everybody. Okay... excuse me?

28:48.601 --> 28:50.602
Everyone, come back, please.

28:50.637 --> 28:52.871
You... in the blue? Can
someone get her attention?

28:52.906 --> 28:56.375
Please. Okay, now who has the ball?

28:56.409 --> 28:58.377
Who has the imaginary ball?

28:59.746 --> 29:01.413
You stay here, okay?

29:07.620 --> 29:10.189
- Hello.
- Hey.

29:11.257 --> 29:13.225
You and Toby in the same week.

29:13.259 --> 29:16.495
- It must be my birthday.
- Yeah, I wanted to talk to you about that.

29:18.331 --> 29:21.400
You know, I don't even hear
from you people for six years,

29:21.434 --> 29:24.169
and the day you show up,
you ask me for a favor?

29:24.204 --> 29:26.071
Calling you wasn't my idea.

29:26.105 --> 29:27.940
I tried to talk him out of it.

29:27.974 --> 29:29.975
- I thought we had a nice meeting.
- Oh yeah?

29:30.009 --> 29:32.177
Is that what you think?
You think it was nice?

29:32.212 --> 29:33.946
He asked you to make one call.

29:33.980 --> 29:36.048
- I know what he asked me.
- Then why couldn't you do it

29:36.082 --> 29:38.650
without all the little digs?

29:38.685 --> 29:40.018
I told him I'd make the call

29:40.053 --> 29:42.688
<i>after he beefed up his resume.</i>

29:42.722 --> 29:44.723
You weren't supposed to critique him.

29:44.757 --> 29:47.459
He wasn't asking for your opinion.

29:47.494 --> 29:48.894
Maybe, just maybe,

29:48.928 --> 29:50.863
he wanted a little support.

29:50.897 --> 29:53.632
He's got some stiff competition.
If he can't take that...

29:53.666 --> 29:56.368
Oh yeah... yeah right. Yeah.

29:56.402 --> 29:59.238
The Bill Kennish no-bull straight talk.

29:59.272 --> 30:02.207
Well, thank you for being the only person

30:02.242 --> 30:04.176
to tell it to him like it really is.

30:04.210 --> 30:06.245
You turned out all right.

30:06.279 --> 30:08.447
You can't take credit for me.

30:08.481 --> 30:11.250
What I've done, I've done in spite of you.

30:11.284 --> 30:13.118
(Chuckles)

30:13.152 --> 30:16.288
You came all the way out here to
pick that same old fight with me?

30:16.322 --> 30:18.891
Some things just never change, do they?

30:20.860 --> 30:23.795
You know,

30:23.830 --> 30:26.698
every once in a while I ask
myself if I did the right thing

30:26.733 --> 30:28.967
keeping you out of my kids' lives.

30:29.002 --> 30:32.604
And I just want to thank you
for removing any of that doubt

30:32.639 --> 30:34.506
once and for all.

30:41.405 --> 30:43.862
Yes. Hello. I was hoping to speak with Cindy.

30:46.026 --> 30:47.994
Hi, Cindy, this is Regina Vasquez.

30:48.028 --> 30:50.696
We met yesterday about
the receptionist position?

30:52.666 --> 30:54.834
Oh, you filled it.

30:56.537 --> 30:57.770
Uh-huh, right.

30:57.805 --> 31:00.606
Well, I mean, I don't have
specific receptionist experience

31:00.641 --> 31:02.922
but I ran my own business for
12 years, which I thought...

31:06.680 --> 31:08.714
Well, if you have any other openings...

31:11.218 --> 31:12.618
(Sighs)

31:12.653 --> 31:14.554
