33:36.730 --> 33:39.932
That mean girl? Her opinion
means that much to you?

33:39.967 --> 33:42.702
I'm sorry, I wasn't thinking.

33:42.736 --> 33:44.637
I have feelings, Bay.

33:44.671 --> 33:47.673
I am not just a robot
who just provides for you

33:47.708 --> 33:50.443
and then disappears
until you need me again.

33:50.477 --> 33:51.644
Mom... mom!

33:55.282 --> 33:56.549
That's not what I think.

33:56.583 --> 33:59.218
You think that because I am not artistic

33:59.252 --> 34:01.454
or independent enough for you,

34:01.488 --> 34:04.190
you don't have to be
kind to me or supportive?

34:06.126 --> 34:07.994
Bay, I did this for you.

34:08.027 --> 34:09.395
No, you didn't.

34:09.429 --> 34:11.931
I'm sorry, mom, but you did this for you.

34:11.965 --> 34:14.000
You asked me to save your drama club!

34:14.034 --> 34:16.135
I didn't ask you to
join it! It was my thing.

34:19.840 --> 34:23.042
In two years you're going to
be out of the house forever.

34:25.045 --> 34:27.913
And this that we have together right now?

34:27.947 --> 34:29.715
It's going to be gone.

